c: 4
v: 127
t: "Uye vanokubvunza izvo zvinobvumidzwa pavakadzi. Taura kuti: “Allah vanokurairai maererano navo, uye maererano neizvo zvamunoverengerwa muGwaro maererano nenherera sikana avo vamusingapi chidimbu chakatarwa (cheMahr, Chipo chinobviswa nemurume achipa mudzimai wake pakuroorana, nenhaka) asi muchida kuvaroora, uye maererano nevana vadiki vasina simba rekuzvidzivirira uye vanodzvinyirirwa, uye kuti muve nesimba kuva munoenzanisa kunherera. Uye chose chakanaka chamunoita, Allah vanochiziva"